  Locus:
    Page: 57
    Verse: 20
Tags:
  - Children
---
So long as one does not become simple like a child, one does not get divine
illumination. Forget all the worldly knowledge that you have acquired and
become as ignorant as a child, and then you will get the divine wisdom.
